==English==

===Etymology===
Turkish, from Arabic {{ARchar|[[عبريق]]}} ''‘ibrīq'', from Persian {{FAchar|[[ابريز]]}} ''ābrīz'', from {{FAchar|[[اب]]}} ''āb'' ‘water’ + {{FAchar|[[ريز]]}} ''rīz'' ‘cup’.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ɪb'ri:k/}}

===Noun===
